"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-07-27-extremely-disrespectful-elon-musk-slams-drag-queens-parody-of-last-supper-at-paris-olympics\", \"text\": \"Published  on  By  American billionaire businessman, Elon Musk, has joined millions around the world to criticise Drag Queen's alleged mockery of Christianity at the opening ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.  DAILY POST reports that an attempt by Drag Queen to recreate da Vinci's painting of Jesus' Last Supper during the Olympic Games opening ceremony has sparked a worldwide uproar, especially from Christians who labelled it \\\"a blasphemy.\\\"  Commenting under one of the post on X, Musk, who is a self-proclaimed atheist, said it was \\\"extremely disrespectful\\\" to Christians.  He wrote, \\\"This was extremely disrespectful to Christians.\\\"  Senator Ifeanyi Ubah is dead  Beyonc\\u00e9 introduces Team USA at 2024 Paris Olympics  Elon Musk sparks online debate after saying 'money can not buy happiness'  Elon Musk rants as Spain investigates Grok, Instagram, TikTok  UK investigates Elon Musk's X, Grok AI amid France probe  Elon Musk summoned as France probes X, Grok AI  Elon Musk announces X to make recommendation algorithm public in 7 days  Nicolas Maduro: Venezuela can now have prosperity - Elon Musk congratulates Trump  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\"}"